highlights.text: “THATS WHAT I WANT” by Lil Nas X is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #3.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 242 weeks straight.
Lil Nas X has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “INDUSTRY BABY (feat. Jack Harlow)” is the highest at #2.
“love nwantiti (ah ah ah)” by CKay is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 141 spots at #32.
